le-east-news/iran/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/iranian-generals-assassination-signals-a-dangerous-turn-in-israels-northern-front/0000018e-9b3f-d64e-afce-ffbf18780000</guid></item><item><title>“人们不断咒骂辛瓦尔”：反对哈马斯的加沙人确信他们是大多数</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/people-are-cursing-sinwar-gazans-opposing-hamas-are-sure-theyre-the-majority/0000018e-9ada-dfd2-afce-deff025f0000</link><description>接受《国土报》采访的四名加沙人对加沙地带的哈马斯领导人以及 10 月 7 日发动战争的决定表示不满。他们说，许多人担心哈马斯会因为他们的言论而惩罚他们，并指责阿拉伯媒体在报道时视而不见。有人批评该团体</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 19:15:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/people-are-cursing-sinwar-gazans-opposing-hamas-are-sure-theyre-the-majority/0000018e-9ada-dfd2-afce-deff025f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在全麻下成功接受疝气手术</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-undergoes-successful-hernia-operation-under-full-anesthesia/0000018e-9ad1-d64e-afce-fff5513b0000</link><description>据他的办公室称，内塔尼亚胡完全清醒，状况良好，并被转移到康复病房</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 19:07:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-undergoes-successful-hernia-operation-under-full-anesthesia/0000018e-9ad1-d64e-afce-fff5513b0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗誓言对以色列高级将领在大马士革被杀一事作出“严厉”反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-01/ty-article/iran-blames-israel-for-syria-strike-threatens-harsh-response-for-killing-of-top-general/0000018e-9a50-d64e-afce-fff552490000</link><description>伊朗革命卫队表示，有七名革命卫队成员在袭击中丧生，而以色列拒绝就这一事件发表评论。这次袭击杀死了一名曾在黎巴嫩和叙利亚领导精锐圣城军的伊朗高级军事顾问</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 17:04:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-01/ty-article/iran-blames-israel-for-syria-strike-threatens-harsh-response-for-killing-of-top-general/0000018e-9a50-d64e-afce-fff552490000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 178 天：以色列逮捕哈马斯领导人哈尼亚的亲属</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-178-israel-arrests-relative-of-hamas-leader-haniyeh/0000018e-9a87-dd2b-ad9f-dadf84280000</link><description>据报道，以色列对伊朗大马士革大使馆发动的袭击造成六人死亡，其中包括革命卫队高级指挥官 ■ 以色列军队在两周行动后从 Al-Shifa 医院撤出 ■ 以色列和美国官员将就以色列国防军可能对拉法发动地面进攻举行虚拟会议 ■ 三人以色列南部地区发生刺伤袭击，以色列人受伤 ■ 战争结束 178 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 16:55:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-178-israel-arrests-relative-of-hamas-leader-haniyeh/0000018e-9a87-dd2b-ad9f-dadf84280000</guid></item></channel></rss>